    "Details": "The DG1-O is the standard configuration of the Dengier OmniMech, designed to handle a broad range of battlefield situations. An LB-10X autocannon and Snub-Nose PPC provide solid direct fire output while a Streak SRM 2 and ER Medium Laser add close-range bite. Two Heavy Machine Guns handle anti-infantry duties and a Hatchet gives it genuine melee threat. CASE II protects the ammunition bay throughout.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Protected Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
